/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling street scene in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the cityscape. The sky above is a clear blue, with power lines crisscrossing across it, adding a geometric contrast to the natural elements. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. In the distance, a few trees can be seen, their green foliage providing a touch of nature amidst the urban environment. The image is slightly distorted due to the fisheye lens effect, adding a unique perspective to the photograph. The colors in the image are vibrant, with the blue of the sky and the green of the trees standing out against the more muted tones of the buildings.
